import React,{useState, useEffect} from "react"
function Meme() {
    
    return(
        <form className="meme-form">
            <input 
            type="text"
            id="topText"
            name="topText"
            className="top-text"
             />
                      
            <input 
            type="text"
            id="bottomText"
            name="bottomText"
            className="bottom-text"
             />
            <input 
            type="submit"
            id="bottomText"
            name="bottomText"
            className="btn-btn"
             />
             <label>Get meme image</label>

                      
        </form>
    )
}
export default Meme
